

 *****************  /usr/ipsc/examples/rmfort_vx/README  ********************


    This directory contains example programs designed to demonstrate
    VX functionality.  Two sub-directories, vx287host and vx287node,
    are designed to show VX functionality on the host and a standard
    iPSC cube.  Additional sub-directories will be present if the optional
    vector (vx) and/or vast software has been installed.  These contain
    programs designed to run on a VX machine.

